{% extends 'base.html' %}
{% load static %}
{% block extra_title %}About HENDOSHI{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<style>
.about-buttons .btn-pink {
    color: #000 !important;
    text-decoration: none !important;
}
</style>
<div class="vault-page">
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<!-- Standard Site Hero (products/new drops/vault style) -->
		<section class="vault-hero">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-12 text-center">
						<img src="{% static 'images/pug-skull.webp' %}" alt="HENDOSHI Pug Skull" class="pug-skull-branding mb-3" loading="lazy">
						<h1 class="vault-hero-title">About HENDOSHI</h1>
						<p class="vault-hero-subtitle">WEAR YOUR WEIRD — No Filler. Just Killer.</p>
						<div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-4 flex-wrap">
							<a href="{% url 'new_drops' %}" class="btn btn-pink">New Drops</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- About Content Section -->
		<section class="contact-form-section py-5">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row justify-content-center">
					<div class="col-12">
						<div class="contact-card">
							<div class="profile-card about-vibrant">
								<p class="lead">HENDOSHI was built for people who never fit the template and never wanted to. We live at the crossroads of heavy metal, gothic art, gym culture, dark humor, and pure creative chaos. Our designs smash skulls, lift iron, shred guitars, worship weird animals, melt reality, and laugh while doing it. This brand was never meant to be subtle. It's meant to hit hard.</p>

								<div class="two-columns">
									<div>
										<h3><i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i> What We Make</h3>
										<p>Every piece we create pulls from tattoo flash, old-school thrash metal album covers, gritty gym motivation, surreal nightmares, and sarcastic humor. Skeletons deadlift. Animals wear battle armor. Skulls glow, burn, and glitch. Nothing here is accidental. Nothing here is safe.</p>
									</div>
									<div>
										<h3><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How We Do It</h3>
										<p>HENDOSHI is for the ones who train heavy, think deep, dress loud, and refuse to blend in. We don't follow trends. We don't soften edges. We don't add filler. We make apparel for misfits, outsiders, and people who wear their identity like armor.</p>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="about-buttons">
									<a href="{% url 'products' %}" class="btn btn-pink">Browse Designs</a>
									<a href="{% url 'vault:vault_gallery' %}" class="btn btn-pink">Explore The Vault</a>
								</div>

								<hr class="muted-hr">

								<blockquote class="about-quote">"Wear your weird. No filler. Just killer."</blockquote>

								<div class="about-grid">
									<div class="about-card glassmorphic-card">
										<h4><i class="fas fa-users"></i> For Misfits</h4>
										<p>We exist for people who don't fit neatly into boxes and never wanted to. Metalheads, goths, gym rats, powerlifters, coders, book lovers, festival goers, animal lovers, and proud misfits.</p>
									</div>
									<div class="about-card glassmorphic-card">
										<h4><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> No Filler</h4>
										<p>We don't add filler. Every design is killer. Printed on demand to maintain quality and availability, just like our community.</p>
									</div>
									<div class="about-card glassmorphic-card">
										<h4><i class="fas fa-music"></i> Anti-Corporate</h4>
										<p>No corporate fluff. No polite marketing. We speak like a friend in the mosh pit — rebellious, witty, and real.</p>
									</div>
								</div>

								<p class="tight">Questions? Collabs? Hate mail? Hit us — <a href="{% url 'contact' %}">Contact Us</a>.</p>

								<p class="small muted">Designed with grit and printed on demand for killer quality. Sizing tips: order true to size, unless you're planning to crowd surf.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

